      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>waxy potatoes</strong> in half lengthways</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong> to a pot of plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, cook for 15-20 min or until fork-tender, then drain and return to the pot</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
