    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the beef mixture has thickened, season with a grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and discard the <strong>bay leaf[ves]</strong>,<strong> </strong>transfer it to an <strong>oven-proof dish </strong>and reserve the pan</p><p>Top the beef mixture with the <strong>rosemary potatoes </strong>and sprinkle over the<strong> reserved rosemary leaves</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 20 min or until golden and bubbling – this is your<strong> hearty beef, carrot & mustard pie</strong></p>",
