    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spring greens</strong> then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Rip the leaves off the <strong>spring greens</strong>, discard the tough stalks, then layer the leaves over each other, roll them up and slice into thin strips</p><p>Once the pie is almost done, wipe the reserved pan clean and add to a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced spring greens </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until tender</p>",
